    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the paint is even and strong throughout. The interior shows no meaningful wear \u2014 upholstery, surfaces, and controls are all in like-new condition. Mechanically, the car runs and drives without issue. A clean, well-preserved example.",
      "price": 46000.0,
